    <div class="flow kc-portfolio-items">
      <h2>Items</h2>
      {
            portfolioPosts.map((project) => (
          <Heading tag="h3" size="h3">
            {project.data.title}
          </Heading>
          <p>Test</p>
        ))
      }
      <!-- Algonquin College -->
      <div class="flow kc-portfolio-item">
        <div class="grid" data-layout="50-50">
          <Heading tag="h3" size="h3">Algonquin College</Heading>
          <div class="content flow prose">
            <p>In 2024, I was part of a team that designed and built the Algonquin College Design System. This system is used by the college to ensure consistency and accessibility across all their digital products.</p>
            <p>My role included designing components, creating documentation, and ensuring that the system met accessibility standards.</p>
